OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FTurning very
OL,6,Fwindy, with inland gales, especially
OL,7,Fover hills. Occasional blustery
OL,8,Fshowers likely, mainly before
OL,9,Fmidnight, and again towards dawn.
OL,10,FWinds also easing through the early
OL,11,Fhours of Easter Sunday, but staying
OL,12,Frather breezy and cloudy.
OL,13,
OL,14,CSunday:FA rather cloudy day, but some
OL,15,Fbrighter or sunny spells are possible.
OL,16,FOccasional blustery showers will
OL,17,Fcontinue, but largely clearing by the
OL,18,Fearly afternoon. A little cooler than
OL,19,FSaturday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
